Heggie & Hut 
The Gravitational Million-Body Problem (Cambridge, 2003)
Appendix A (pp.306): A Simple N-Body Integrator

https://ui.adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2003gmbp.book.....H

BIBCODE:  2003gmbp.book.....H

Historic notes:
  nbody.m      Original version, written by D. Heggie (help by Chris Eilbeck?)
  nbody.c      Version provided by Simon Portegies Zwart
  nbody_hh.c   SPZ's version, with a simple CLI, adopted by Peter Teuben


Benchmark is 1024 particles , 10 dumps, tstop=1.0
Compilation default is "gcc -g -O2"

